data.description: Lovely neighborhood in the Ponderosa School District, close to Spokane River, Q'emlin Park, and Black Bay Park with RV Parking on a cul-de-sac street!     This 4 bedroom 2 bath home was designed with the main floor being JUST for the living area, with a large vaulted ceiling, great room, big picture windows with updated appliances in the kitchen. Upstairs from the main area is your master bedroom with vaulted ceilings as well with full bath, and secondary bedroom.  Downstairs from the main living area, is another full bedroom, and a 4th (non-conforming) room/utility with two built in bunkbeds, and another full bath.  Fresh paint throughout home with a rear yard that is fully fenced, landscaped, fruit trees, firepit and sprinklers front and back. On the RV parking side, there is a double access gate for further storage of all your toys.
